<section class="relative py-24 sm:py-32 lg:py-40">
  <div class="max-w-[42rem] mx-auto px-6 sm:px-10 text-center">
    <span
      class="inline-block px-4 py-1.5 rounded-full bg-lavender-100/50 text-lavender-600 text-xs font-semibold tracking-[0.15em] uppercase mb-7"
      data-animate
    >
      What is Clearva
    </span>

    <h2
      class="font-display text-[2.25rem] sm:text-[2.75rem] lg:text-[3.25rem] text-lavender-900 leading-[1.12] tracking-tight mb-8"
      data-animate
      style="transition-delay: 80ms"
    >
      Mental health support that feels like it's on your side
    </h2>

    <div class="space-y-5 text-[1.0625rem] sm:text-lg text-gray-500 leading-[1.75]" data-animate style="transition-delay: 160ms">
      <p>
        Clearva creates a space where you can talk openly about how you're feeling
        — without judgment, without pressure, and without needing to have the right words.
        Through guided conversation, it helps you make sense of your emotions, understand
        patterns in your wellbeing, and find support that fits your life.
      </p>
      <p class="text-gray-400">
        It's not therapy. It's not a diagnosis. It's a companion for the moments
        when you need to pause and check in with yourself.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
